data.description: Charming home, nested in a quiet pocket between Ryan Lake and Victory Memorial Parkway. Featuring two bedrooms and a full bath on the main, a large finished upper level with a tall ceiling and perfect for use of an owners suite, guest bedroom, home office, game room or whatever needs you may have. Basement is a clean slate and has potential for additional finished square feet. Yard is spacious with a large deck and additional parking in the back. Close proximity to schools, parks, recreation trails, restaurants, coffee shops, grocery stores, off leash dog park, lakes, highway access and more. Come see for yourself and welcome home!
